{"tid":2233175,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鍾國斌指警控罪不符 「港人憂國安法濫捕」","createTime":"2020-10-07T02:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T05:18:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a4786e4a3c07fc529ef3039d2e03c8a1fe47377f","tid":2233175,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T02:44:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/32VJAHGYJJCY3ERDNTSDV3W2YQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2F32VJAHGYJJCY3ERDNTSDV3W2YQ%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmRUAsmJrpgm%2FsQZzOZZuI0I%3D&h=5740eee3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2F32VJAHGYJJCY3ERDNTSDV3W2YQ%2F&h=f364799c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/32VJAHGYJJCY3ERDNTSDV3W2YQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n鍾國斌指警控罪不符<br />\n「港人憂國安法濫捕」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1Cvt8uisJ0hs6JR72bzNof9M_tc=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HCW6VCVPRJDUTHQC6BH7GLBZE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1Cvt8uisJ0hs6JR72bzNof9M_tc%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHCW6VCVPRJDUTHQC6BH7GLBZE4.jpg&h=a9290a9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鍾國斌<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警隊近月多次以港版國家安全法採取拘捕行動，自由黨立法會議員鍾國斌（圖）接受無綫明珠台《清心直說》訪問時形容，很多香港市民不明白，為何警方以國安法拘捕市民，卻未有以港版國安法提告，令人對國安法推行及落實感擔心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n倘局勢不變 對建制無好處<br />\n<br />\n鍾國斌在節目中說，國安法本身並沒有問題，此法落實後，香港社會也變得平靜下來，他只是擔心此法在推行和落實的問題。他指，有些例子可見警方嘗試以港版國安法拘捕市民，但最終不能使用，他認為警方應使用其他法例，而非國安法，也有很多香港市民不明白，警方為何使用國安法拘捕市民，但卻以其他法例控告。<br />\n<br />\n對於本屆立法會延任一年，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至於政府計劃修改法例，容許港人在大灣區投票，鍾國斌指政府將提出有關方案，自由黨會否同意，要視乎法案內容。他說，如果有人認為容許港人在香港以外地方投票是不符《基本法》，大可進行司法覆核，但他同時指，由於未來一年的立法會只有九個月，所以屆時所有法案又要由從頭再來，故有關容許港人在大灣區投票理論上和技術上是不能通過。<br />\n<br />\n鍾又稱，如果一年後香港的氣氛繼續與現時一樣，。。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"ebe10a417e2eb38b833e6b07c61c028f6ced12d1","tid":2233175,"uid":144541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T03:39:05.000Z","msg":"商家佬心水清"},{"pid":"004dcae497699cc36573ffdeb0c2988e464aa337","tid":2233175,"uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T03:40:04.000Z","msg":"批評國安，拉得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133ca62c4cb4598bf2877c65e099163dc42ea500","tid":2233175,"uid":54125,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T03:48:56.000Z","msg":"一早話咗叫你哋唔好奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家先識驚"},{"pid":"8cff8a430029e480bb2cc7dfc621ce0eb336e458","tid":2233175,"uid":230104,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T03:53:38.000Z","msg":"因為鍾國賓唔識團長<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fvScGkM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfvScGkM.jpg&h=a9ab7f47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89650acc4ac97a33f59ec5e2d7fffce3fa68223a","tid":2233175,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T03:54:02.000Z","msg":"反對國安法要DQ, 質疑國安法使唔使DQ?"},{"pid":"c12d8d6b0bdfb3432a5f13f1d5a4e71a68b7443c","tid":2233175,"uid":259901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T03:55:51.000Z","msg":"議員對國安法說三道四指手劃腳已經犯咗國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6306e97ad383de9e3ca6214bb3b38334cced17","tid":2233175,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cff8a430029e480bb2cc7dfc621ce0eb336e458","tid":2233175,"uid":230104,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T03:53:38.000Z","msg":"因為鍾國賓唔識團長<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fvScGkM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfvScGkM.jpg&h=a9ab7f47&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T03:56:5